<h3 id="WhatIsTheMeaningOfOm&amp;Aum?">What Is The Meaning Of Om &amp; Aum?</h3>
They say that before the world began, Brahma ‚Äì the creator, the absolute reality ‚Äì was one, and He said, ‚ÄúI am one, but may I become many?‚Äù This thought created a vibration that settled into a sound. This sound was Om. The creation of the world began with this vibration ‚Äì Om.

